                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Please take this up on the mailing list, not in the issue tracker.\r\n\r\nWe have many good reasons for introducing auto-escaping, and many have been discussed in the past (the main reason it wasn't implemented in the v1 series is that by the time the discussion came up, we were already poised to release 1.0 stable). \r\n\r\nIf you feel strongly that auto-escaping should not be an option, then you need to outline your arguments on the mailing list, and allow for discussion.",
